message.entry: Passing an object of the scatteredInterpolant class as an input argument to the entry-point function is not supported during code generation.
Code generation does not support creating empty scatteredInterpolant objects.
Code generation only supports 2-dimensional interpolation with scatteredInterpolant.
The behavior of the generated code might differ from MATLAB because the query point {0}, {1} lies in a degenerate or sliver triangle.
The behavior of the generated code might differ from MATLAB because the delaunay triangulation generated by Qhull contains degenerate or sliver triangles.
